name: SubstanceProtein.subunit.subunit
title: SubstanceProtein.subunit.subunit
purpose: Data Elements are defined for each element to assist in questionnaire construction etc

element.short: Index of primary sequences of amino acids linked through peptide bonds in order of decreasing length. Sequences of the same length will be ordered by molecular weight. Subunits that have identical sequences will be repeated and have sequential subscripts
element.definition: Index of primary sequences of amino acids linked through peptide bonds in order of decreasing length. Sequences of the same length will be ordered by molecular weight. Subunits that have identical sequences will be repeated and have sequential subscripts.
